    docs(028): peck-teachings-adoption packet — analysis, phased plan, deep research
    
    Add the 028-peck-teachings-adoption spec packet (analysis + research only; no spec-kit source changed):
    - 001: peck-teachings analysis (which peck mechanisms map to spec-kit gaps) + 5-iteration deep-research report (cli-opencode gpt-5.5 xhigh) with synthesis, iterations, deltas, state.
    - 002 (T3 self-check template blocks), 003 (T4 current-state advisory rule), 004 (T2 constitutional-rule review surface): planned phases, refined by the research.
    - T1 (AC-coverage completion gate) intentionally deferred to a future packet.
    Strict-validated: parent + 4 children, 0 errors / 0 warnings.
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>

